907, 34.1279, 30.157, 33.2696, 34.2857, 35.3833, 35.4347, 34.2794, 34.8501, 35.5426, 36.4193, 33.8127, 40.3395, 43.0703, 38.4381, 37.0202, 38.1342, 38.7946, 39.3458, 37.8825, 37.7571, 39.2831, 39.0534, 39.5054, 39.3303, 41.003, 42.8458, 43.0487, 44.3981, 43.5436, 43.6725, 44.4428, 45.1084, 42.6002, 43.9728, 44.7268, 42.6578, 43.0546, 41.6243, 41.8647, 41.1617, 43.3738, 41.9032, 41.4996, 42.9617, 44.6939, 45.2468, 49.6332, 50.4134, 49.6255, 50.1027, 49.4865, 51.9124, 50.8635, 51.2815, 52.9112, 51.8245, 50.3326, 54.2503, 53.9267, 53.2231, 51.4501, 52.1985, 50.7184, 50.8543, 49.0956, 48.7388, 47.9801, 47.2003, 45.7851, 45.1935, 45.6801, 46.1188, 45.3468, 46.5696, 46.4629, 46.0423, 43.4665, 44.8999, 44.9536, 45.4793, 43.8942, 43.666, 44.3189, 43.7153, 42.212, 42.0643, 42.3409, 41.8513, 41.6068, 40.368, 40.8852, 38.8157, 36.1071, 34.7301, 33.0366, 32.1877, 30.1915, 29.106, 29.4697, 30.7471, 29.5669, 33.0062, 33.1165, 33.9678, 34.1235, 33.7087, 31.8201, 30.6507, 30.523, 31.3954, 30.6977, 30.4265, 28.5588, 29.8514, 29.315, 26.4202, 29.7007, 29.1806, 27.5915, 27.7768, 29.6601, 27.3751, 28.9801, 29.783, 29.8605, 31.4245, 35.1059, 34.7193, 34.3455, 34.246, 36.847, 36.6158, 36.0499, 36.8337, 36.8831, 38.7778, 40.7429, 38.332, 39.0338, 40.8032, 41.7861, 40.5112, 40.4338, 40.3549, 39.0355, 37.6053, 34.3668, 37.1881, 36.4797, 36.7296, 35.8207, 35.532, 35.2801, 29.8567, 29.8072, 29.3403, 29.0589, 27.5818, 30.373, 28.193, 27.001, 28.752, 29.5755, 31.389], "summary_html": "<h1>行业有效量价因子与行业轮动策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略从华西证券的行业量价因子研报中提取了 11 个因子，分属动量、交易波动、换手率、多空对比、量价背离、量幅同向六大类。研报原文针对 A 股中信一级行业做截面轮动，我们将因子逻辑迁移至商品期货品种维度，用日频量价数据计算各因子的截面排名，等权合成为综合信号后做多空交易。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑是：量价背离（成交量和价格反向变化）、低波动（交易稳定性）、动量期限结构（长期趋势去除短期拥挤）等因子在截面上对品种未来收益有预测力。通过多因子等权组合分散单因子风险，配合 IC gate 过滤弱品种和波动率目标缩放控制风险敞口。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>0.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.3%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-23.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.16</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.24 / 0.16</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.22</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.75</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.47</span></td><td>0.08</td><td>1.48</td><td>1.34</td><td>0.31</td><td>1.36</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td>0.09</td><td>1.13</td><td>0.44</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.56</span></td><td>0.05</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.1</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>因子 1: 二阶动量</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_1 = \\text{EWMA}\\left(\\frac{C_t - \\bar{C}_{w}}{{\\bar{C}_{w}}} - \\text{delay}\\left(\\frac{C_t - \\bar{C}_{w}}{{\\bar{C}_{w}}}, \\frac{w}{2}\\right), w\\right)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 2: 动量期限差</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_2 = \\frac{C_t - C_{t-L}}{C_{t-L}} - \\frac{C_t - C_{t-S}}{C_{t-S}}, \\quad L &gt; S</div>\n<p><strong>因子 3/4: 交易波动</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_3 = -\\text{STD}(\\text{Amount}, w), \\quad F_4 = -\\text{STD}(\\text{Volume}, w)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 5: 换手率变化</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_5 = \\frac{\\text{Mean}(\\text{turnover}, L)}{\\text{Mean}(\\text{turnover}, S)}</div>\n<p><strong>因子 6: 多空对比总量</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_6 = -\\sum_{i=t-w}^{t} \\frac{C_i - L_i}{H_i - C_i}</div>\n<p><strong>因子 7: 多空对比变化</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_7 = \\text{EWMA}\\left(V \\cdot \\frac{(C-L)-(H-C)}{H-L}, L_w\\right) - \\text{EWMA}(\\cdot, S_w)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 8: 量价排序协方差</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_8 = -\\text{corr}(C, V, w)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 9: 量价相关系数</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_9 = -\\text{corr}(C, V, w)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 10: 一阶量价背离</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_{10} = -\\text{corr}\\left(\\text{rank}\\left(\\frac{V_t}{V_{t-1}}-1\\right), \\text{rank}\\left(\\frac{C_t}{O_t}-1\\right), w\\right)</div>\n<p><strong>因子 11: 量幅同向</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F_{11} = \\text{corr}\\left(\\text{rank}\\left(\\frac{V_t}{V_{t-1}}-1\\right), \\text{rank}\\left(\\frac{H_t}{L_t}-1\\right), w\\right)</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>: 各因子截面排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> rank_to_continuous <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1,1]</span> <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 等权平均 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> vol_target_scale <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> rebalance_hold</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.39)</strong>: 初始实现全部 11 个因子，各因子默认窗口 W=20，全部等权合成。最优单因子为动量期限差 (Sharpe 0.39) 和成交金额波动 (0.39)。截面 IC 和时序 IC 均接近零，信号预测力不足。日均换手率 0.45 过高，交易成本侵蚀显著。诊断显示 SC/RM/BU 等品种大幅亏损。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.82)</strong>: 核心改动是将因子窗口从 W=20 拉长到 W=60，并筛选 top4 因子 (f2/f3/f4/f6) 组合。网格搜索覆盖 W={20,40,60} x hold={21,42} x factor_set={all,top4}。W=60+top4+h21 达到 Sharpe 0.82，通过 backtest gate。换手率从 0.45 降至 0.21。关键发现：长窗口在商品期货上效果明显优于短窗口，top4 因子组合优于全部 11 因子。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.07)</strong>: 在 R2 基础上增加 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种，并扩展因子组合到 top6 (加入 f8 量价排序协方差和 f10 一阶量价背离)。同时测试 W=80 和 _cs/_ts 归一化变体。最终 <code>combo_w60_t6_h21_ic</code> 达 Sharpe 1.07。<strong>关键转折</strong>: IC gate 过滤掉了 35% 弱品种，使信号集中在有效品种上，Sharpe 从 0.73 (无 IC gate 的 w60_t6) 提升至 1.07。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货 (58 品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 月频再平衡 (21 个交易日)</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 前半段 (2016-2020) Sharpe 1.87 vs 后半段 (2021-2025) Sharpe 0.59，近年表现衰减明显\n<p>- 2023-2024 年度 Sharpe 为负，策略可能处于低谷期 - 与因子库最相似因子 (zhongxin_combo) 相关性 0.47，属于边际水平 - 研报原文是股票行业轮动策略，迁移到商品期货后因子逻辑仍然有效但强度有所下降</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 未验证</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 未记录</li>\n</ul>"}